overview:
Vestiigo is an online career site that connects young professionals with top careers.

Vestiigo connects the career-savvy professional with the latest job opportunities at Canada’s best and brightest companies. If you’re a university graduate with at least two years of professional experience, prefer dealing directly with employers instead of recruitment agencies and like the idea of a service that hand picks every career opportunity it lists, then this is the site for you.
